  - DISTRICT BASELINE LOCKED
  - RURAL-URBAN NETWORK ACTIVE
  - CANDIDATE SYSTEM AUDITED
  milestoneMessages:
  - MLA record, issue map and candidate criteria verified. Ab leadership bench and
    zone coordinators build karo.
  - Leadership cohort, rural-urban desks and selection decision complete. Funding
    and information discipline next hai.
  - Funding, fact-check and public convention complete. Final compliance district
    readiness decide karega.
